      <title>巴西资产管理公司正在筹备私募信贷基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/private-credit-fund-in-the-works-at-brazil-asset-management-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于普通本地债券利差缩小，挤压了较为传统基金的收益，巴西最大的保险公司之一的资产管理部门 SulAmerica Investimentos 正在筹划其首个专注于项目融资的私人信贷基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/private-credit-fund-in-the-works-at-brazil-asset-management-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
